p: Ae. aegypti from Kedougou and exposed to DENV-4 survived better until 9 dpbm, then mortality increased highly compared to controls from the 11th dpbm. Mosquitoes exposed to DENV-1 had reduced survival early compared to DENV-3 and DENV-4. From the 11 th dpbm, survival of Ae. aegypti from Kedougou was significantly affected by all three DENV serotypes.
